9d681facdde50a589b6cb7ac07002cdbb13d9f38.commit.message:
Converted to use the new linked list.

Fixed removeAll problem.  The AbstractMemoryCache was only clearing the map.  Any subclasses that didn't implement removeAll would have full lists and empty maps.  This solves a major memory problem.
